{"tid":225221,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有小聰明但係又懶嘅你入一入嚟","createTime":"2017-05-01T15:29:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T17:24:17.000Z","uid":4210,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"41205557a75790f0a685347d692f72860bcfb3ea","tid":225221,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:29:57.000Z","msg":"前幾日俾個人屌醒咗我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n是咁的 佢話因為我做乜嘢都可以好易上手<br />\n出少少力就已經可以做得比一般人好 所以咪淨係甘於咁 所以咪懶<br />\n所以咪會睇唔起其他人 又受唔起壓力<br />\n一有個大壓力咪無啦啦跳制有情緒病。<br />\n之後我又好擅長用自己嘅情緒病威迫人哋唔好再逼我俾壓力我<br />\n<br />\n咁因為我係做表演的 跟住佢又話我做舞台劇、做表演都係咁<br />\n我身為一個演員將我放上台面其實係好好睇 <br />\n明明只要我俾力就可以比任何人都做得好<br />\n但係因為自己比少少力已經可以做好過一般表演者 所以就真係只係比少少力...<br />\n之後佢提我唔改左佢就好難比自己做得更好<br />\n<br />\n希望各位同我一樣 真係唔好再因為自己啲惰性浪費咗自己嘅天賦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有心改絕對唔會怕遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddfe1046076740d92c132dceae471d8d5613fe83","tid":225221,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:33:34.000Z","msg":"冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f766c08b64a5a52f4a5a3ec7722f8aa3755597f","tid":225221,"uid":94548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:34:28.000Z","msg":"一路懶緊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 相信唔懶既話一定生活都豐富d.."},{"pid":"cc725601081fc4ffdb350e4a42fce4ac7a248a0b","tid":225221,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:37:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一路懶緊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 相信唔懶既話一定生活都豐富d..</blockquote><br />\n唔好俾藉口自己懶 改啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6968e66d02e10b84b53a63b849e607ea6f15772f","tid":225221,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:38:20.000Z","msg":"根本一認真做好少少就叻過其他人，跟住就會懶，到覺得差過人地既時候，再發力又追得返，之後又懶過⋯<br />\n由細到大都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"367c388a61b32d31de01f48af56a042e6673fd56","tid":225221,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:41:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本一認真做好少少就叻過其他人，跟住就會懶，到覺得差過人地既時候，再發力又追得返，之後又懶過⋯<br />\n由細到大都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以咪睇下你想過得舒服啲定係想做乜都要最好"},{"pid":"4b3b8788b57db13c3bf5e9d9f8875ccdd7bfc4f6","tid":225221,"uid":29740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:47:00.000Z","msg":"唔關事,搵到自己鍾意既野就唔會懶,<br />\n只不過你鍾意既野係搵唔到錢,所以先會形成'懶'依個字<br />\n睇得明就睇得明,睇唔明就算"},{"pid":"108dc283c60bf6b876c659cd9f745da30880fa33","tid":225221,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T16:22:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔關事,搵到自己鍾意既野就唔會懶,<br />\n只不過你鍾意既野係搵唔到錢,所以先會形成'懶'依個字<br />\n睇得明就睇得明,睇唔明就算</blockquote><br />\n我諗20年之後我會明"},{"pid":"eb7babf4f5bfdc139d22a69a34783fe997f895f3","tid":225221,"uid":107215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T16:26:07.000Z","msg":"細個學咩都快過人<br />\n搞到宜家大左周身刀無張利<br />\n學左表面就以為自己識哂"},{"pid":"2300639eb8754b80cf320ffc6d10f508bcbd8e33","tid":225221,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T16:38:13.000Z","msg":"真係懶 完全冇動力去做嘢 成日都明日復明日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c06b997e4dcb70c675b16734b25a91ed4e59ea","tid":225221,"uid":34205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T17:07:54.000Z","msg":"平仔，我都係咁，原來你同我係一樣㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f01fda170f49431ed59543fc027194a576d3ef","tid":225221,"uid":47021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T17:12:03.000Z","msg":"一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做咩都只係出5成力<br />\n用得最多力係dse,都係7成左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1277850f9fa423cbfe239b526934619f4b4b0d7","tid":225221,"uid":48022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T17:14:03.000Z","msg":"改變惰性本身就已經唔係易事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3a4f81f3a44616cdd5edda537e31ac75880d767","tid":225221,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T17:23:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平仔，我都係咁，原來你同我係一樣㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係1定0<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf6502c9a09674cb44b4a59ffd719ffd94bb2de","tid":225221,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T17:24:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>改變惰性本身就已經唔係易事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做乜都得過且過"}]}